{"tid":429731,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得尊敬老人已經係過時既思想？","createTime":"2017-10-09T07:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T20:26:22.000Z","uid":2424,"like":63,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a544d8dcc0a4a15f278192b85753ed5a68dba1","tid":429731,"uid":2424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"古時候尊敬老人呢種思想係源於人隨住年紀增長<br />\n所獲得既經驗同知識會越黎越多<br />\n於是後生既人可以係老人身上學習 唔洗行咁多冤枉路 從而令人類文明穩定咁發展<br />\n但係到左今時今日 人類社會既發展一日千里<br />\n好多時你啊爸啊媽果代既經驗去到你出黎社會之後已經唔適用 更加唔洗講7 80歲妹下妹下果d<br />\n老人已經失去左古時教育後人既作用<br />\n咁尊敬老人呢種思想係咪都應該捨棄呢"},{"pid":"6d84af4158e82ea6ed9e989c19f7fcbcdf4e9610","tid":429731,"uid":83808,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"係值得尊重就唔洗等佢老<br />\n老左先需要尊重<br />\n同乞有咩分別"},{"pid":"12fe4b49dd8506e0fb6a5d41ff9646fb0790033a","tid":429731,"uid":151833,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:56:41.000Z","msg":"依家個個開口埋口都係廢老廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718f3c87ced0d38ca4918ad5f9229fb0a334aa1a","tid":429731,"uid":54733,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"品行先係尊重嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n唔應該因為年紀大所以尊重"},{"pid":"6bdb220dd4d392170b312afeba6bc0ee6e6df6b5","tid":429731,"uid":62167,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"係因為人家有貢獻過社會，所以值得被尊重<br />\n唔關知識事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b5b21f17f198b83bc508678f1a90b0dae0234a","tid":429731,"uid":57962,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea763c9c12dd622aad979a9c057f7db6332e3f5d","tid":429731,"uid":2424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係因為人家有貢獻過社會，所以值得被尊重<br />\n唔關知識事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尊重就對所有人都應該尊重<br />